At its most basic level, amnesia was always intended to wipe both aggro AND the hate list. It needs fixed.<P>and charm basically resets a MOB to a brand new neutral point when it is released. this was a later change to keep released pets from killing casters (rare) or going wild in newbie areas. some people still release their pet than hit it with confuse in rookie zones to be real pricks.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...<P>Please visit our <A HREF="http://www.yesterdayland.com/popopedia/shows/toys/ty1050.php" TARGET=_blank>Sponsors!</A>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
